          <title>
            <string language="sl">Pljučnik</string>
            <string language="en">Lungwort</string>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Lungwort</string>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Lungwort</string>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">Lungwort</string>
            <string language="x-mt-it">Lungwort</string>
            <string language="x-mt-el">Lungwort</string>
            <string language="x-mt-es">Lungwort</string>
          </title>
          <language>x-none</language>
          <description>
            <string language="sl">Korenika tanka. Listi z ostro omejenimi svetlimi pegami; spodnji stebelni listi srčasti ali jajčasti, dlakavi. Raste v gozdovih, med grmovjem, na travnikih, nabrežjih od nižine do gorskega pasu. Družina: srhkolistovke - Boraginaceae.</string>
            <string language="en">Rhizome thin. Leaves with distinctive bright spots. Lower stalk leaves cordate, pilose. It grows in forests, bushes, meadows - from low altitude to mountainous zone. Familiy: Boraginaceae.</string>
          </description>
          <keyword>
            <string language="sl">pljučnik</string>
            <string language="en">lungwort</string>
          </keyword>
          <keyword>
            <string language="sl">rastlina</string>
            <string language="en">plant</string>
          </keyword>
          <keyword>
            <string language="sl">roža</string>
            <string language="en">flower</string>
          </keyword>
          <keyword>
            <string language="sl">pulmonaria officinalis</string>
            <string language="en">pulmonaria officinalis</string>
          </keyword>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Rhizom verdünnen. Blätter mit 
unterscheidenden hellen Punkten. Untererer Stiel verläßt 
cordate, pilose. Er wächst in den Wäldern, Büsche, Wiesen - 
von der niedrigen Höhe zur Gebirgszone. Familiy: 
Boraginaceae.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Le rhizome amincissent. Feuilles avec les 
taches lumineuses distinctives. La tige inférieure part du 
cordate, pilose. Elle se développe dans les forêts, les 
buissons, prés - de basse altitude à la zone montagneuse. 
Familiy : Boraginaceae.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">O rhizome dilui. Folhas com os pontos 
brilhantes distintivos. Um stalk mais baixo sae do cordate, 
pilose. Cresce nas florestas, arbustos, prados - da altura baixa
à zona montanhosa. Familiy: Boraginaceae.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-it">La rizoma si assottiglia. Fogli con i punti
luminosi distintivi. Il gambo più basso lascia il cordate, 
pilose. Si sviluppa in foreste, cespugli, prati - da bassa quota
alla zona montagnosa. Familiy: Boraginaceae.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-el">Ρίζωμα λεπτό. Φύλλα με τα διακριτικά φωτεινά 
σημεία. Ο χαμηλότερος μίσχος αφήνει καρδιοειδής, τριχωτός.
Αυξάνεται στα δάση, οι Μπους, λιβάδια - από το χαμηλό ύψος
στην ορεινή ζώνη. Familiy: Boraginaceae.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-es">El rizoma enrarece. Hojas con los puntos 
brillantes distintivos. Un tallo más bajo sale del cordate, 
pilose. Crece en los bosques, arbustos, prados - de la baja 
altitud a la zona montañosa. Familiy: Boraginaceae.</string>
          </description>
